  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grow Harvest Repeat</strong> is a  2D farming game where you build your farming empire. Take care of your garden, level up skills, and unlock new areas as you progress!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488760/extras/1ba450abb178ce60efeba578fc854377.poster.avif?t=1754577232\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488760/extras/1ba450abb178ce60efeba578fc854377.webm?t=1754577232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488760/extras/1ba450abb178ce60efeba578fc854377.mp4?t=1754577232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Earn by growing plants</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every farming empire starts in the garden — and so does yours. Buy seeds, grow crops, and sell yields - it helps you to get the first coins and will improve your skill. The better your farming skills, the more you can do.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488760/extras/0af4c5f3e0695bc64c571062a58754fa.poster.avif?t=1754577232\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488760/extras/0af4c5f3e0695bc64c571062a58754fa.webm?t=1754577232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488760/extras/0af4c5f3e0695bc64c571062a58754fa.mp4?t=1754577232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Craft goods for sale</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why sell vegetables if you can make more profit selling vegetable salad? Build different devices for crafting. Sell ground coffee,  grilled corn, cheese, and much more. The better your crafting skills, the more profitable goods you can make.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488760/extras/f96c90948f54ce04a0455df29304fc5f.poster.avif?t=1754577232\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488760/extras/f96c90948f54ce04a0455df29304fc5f.webm?t=1754577232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488760/extras/f96c90948f54ce04a0455df29304fc5f.mp4?t=1754577232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build barns and buy animals</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you become an experienced farmer, it's time to invest in livestock. Cows and chickens will bring you milk and eggs. When life gives you milk and eggs, make bread.  And sell it, of course!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grow Harvest Repeat</strong> is a  2D farming game where you build your farming empire. Take care of your garden, level up skills, and unlock new areas as you progress!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488760/extras/1ba450abb178ce60efeba578fc854377.poster.avif?t=1754577232\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488760/extras/1ba450abb178ce60efeba578fc854377.webm?t=1754577232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488760/extras/1ba450abb178ce60efeba578fc854377.mp4?t=1754577232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Earn by growing plants</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every farming empire starts in the garden — and so does yours. Buy seeds, grow crops, and sell yields - it helps you to get the first coins and will improve your skill. The better your farming skills, the more you can do.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488760/extras/0af4c5f3e0695bc64c571062a58754fa.poster.avif?t=1754577232\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488760/extras/0af4c5f3e0695bc64c571062a58754fa.webm?t=1754577232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488760/extras/0af4c5f3e0695bc64c571062a58754fa.mp4?t=1754577232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Craft goods for sale</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why sell vegetables if you can make more profit selling vegetable salad? Build different devices for crafting. Sell ground coffee,  grilled corn, cheese, and much more. The better your crafting skills, the more profitable goods you can make.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488760/extras/f96c90948f54ce04a0455df29304fc5f.poster.avif?t=1754577232\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488760/extras/f96c90948f54ce04a0455df29304fc5f.webm?t=1754577232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488760/extras/f96c90948f54ce04a0455df29304fc5f.mp4?t=1754577232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build barns and buy animals</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you become an experienced farmer, it's time to invest in livestock. Cows and chickens will bring you milk and eggs. When life gives you milk and eggs, make bread.  And sell it, of course!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p>",
